00:26:01.900 --> 00:26:06.070
one of the most important
equations of the last century.

00:26:06.070 --> 00:26:10.360
And it's the equation
we will be solving.

00:26:10.360 --> 00:26:13.720
That's why I think this
history is interesting.

00:26:13.720 --> 00:26:14.660
OK, so there it is.

00:26:14.660 --> 00:26:18.100
So we talked about how
you can take the f out,

00:26:18.100 --> 00:26:21.430
because if H doesn't
depend on time, then

00:26:21.430 --> 00:26:24.780
