00:58:43.810 --> 00:58:45.445
but is an electron
really spinning?

00:58:49.770 --> 00:58:52.320
How does it have
a magnetic moment?

00:58:52.320 --> 00:58:54.420
Let's talk.

00:58:54.420 --> 00:58:58.200
That's a really good
