00:58:58.200 --> 00:59:00.270
And you think about
it as spinning

00:59:00.270 --> 00:59:06.060
because that is our classical
Maxwell sort of ENN framework.

00:59:06.060 --> 00:59:07.680
We think about charged spinning.

00:59:07.680 --> 00:59:08.310
You've done it.

00:59:08.310 --> 00:59:12.930
You make current go through
