00:59:17.670 --> 00:59:19.530
It's sort of like "orbital."

00:59:19.530 --> 00:59:21.810
Should we really be
using the word "orbital?"

00:59:21.810 --> 00:59:25.110
Is this electron orbiting?

00:59:25.110 --> 00:59:27.000
No.

00:59:27.000 --> 00:59:29.950
And that's another
