00:59:58.440 --> 01:00:01.770
And they can only
be up and down,

01:00:01.770 --> 01:00:04.690
only up and down, two values.

01:00:04.690 --> 01:00:09.850
And so what you have is sort
of a new quantum number.

01:00:09.850 --> 01:00:15.040
You have spin, which is
equal to plus or minus 1.

01:00:15.040 --> 01:00:17.890
That's that and that.

01:00:17.890 --> 01:00:19.360
So now each of
these-- and that's

01:00:19.360 --> 01:00:21.490
